## Overview

Compact product tile used in 2×2 category grids within horizontally scrollable carousels. Displays a product image, optional badge, heart/favorite toggle, price, and truncated product name.

**Type**: WCP (Walmart product-level component)
**Location**: `client/components/walmart/WCPItemTile.tsx`
**Styles**: `client/components/walmart/WCPItemTile.module.css`
**Component Library Page**: `/component-library/item-tile`

---

## Import

```tsx
import { WCPItemTile } from '@/components/walmart/WCPItemTile';
import type { WCPItemTileProps, ItemTileBadgeType } from '@/components/walmart/WCPItemTile';
```

---

## Props

| Prop | Type | Required | Default | Description |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| `image` | `string` | Yes | — | Product image URL |
| `name` | `string` | Yes | — | Product name (truncated to 1 line) |
| `price` | `string` | Yes | — | Dollar portion, e.g. `"98"` |
| `cents` | `string` | Yes | — | Cents portion, e.g. `"00"` |
| `originalPrice` | `string` | No | — | Strikethrough price, e.g. `"$200.00"` |
| `pricePrefix` | `string` | No | — | Prefix like `"Now"` — triggers green savings style |
| `priceSuffix` | `string` | No | — | Suffix like `"/mo"` |
| `badge` | `{ label: string; type: ItemTileBadgeType }` | No | — | Optional badge overlay |

---

## Badge Types

```ts
type ItemTileBadgeType = 'bestseller' | 'deal' | 'popular' | 'rollback';
```

| Type | Label example | Visual |
|---|---|---|
| `bestseller` | "Best seller" | Solid red flag |
| `deal` | "Deal" | Light red tint flag |
| `popular` | "Popular pick" | Light blue tint flag |
| `rollback` | "Rollback" | Dark charcoal flag |

---

## Variants

### Default Price

Standard black price text. No prefix, no original price.

```tsx
<WCPItemTile
  image={PRODUCT_IMAGES.airFryer}
  name="Ninja 4 Qt Air Fryer"
  price="98"
  cents="00"
  badge={{ label: 'Best seller', type: 'bestseller' }}
/>
```

### Savings Price

Green price text with "Now" prefix, optional strikethrough original price and suffix.

```tsx
<WCPItemTile
  image={PRODUCT_IMAGES.countertopBlender}
  name="VAVSEA 3-in-1 Blender System"
  price="169"
  cents="98"
  pricePrefix="Now"
  originalPrice="$200.00"
  priceSuffix="/mo"
  badge={{ label: 'Best seller', type: 'bestseller' }}
/>
```

### Plain (No Badge)

Tile without any badge overlay.

```tsx
<WCPItemTile
  image={PRODUCT_IMAGES.mugSet}
  name="Stoneware Mug Set of 4"
  price="28"
  cents="00"
/>
```

