## Anatomy

```
┌─────────────────────────┐
│ [Flag]          [Heart] │  ← absolute positioned overlays
│                         │
│       Product Image     │  ← 145px height, object-fit: contain
│                         │
├─────────────────────────┤
│ Now $169⁹⁸/mo          │  ← price row (green if prefix present)
│ $200.00                 │  ← original price (strikethrough)
│ VAVSEA 3-in-1 Blende…  │  ← product name (1-line clamp)
└─────────────────────────┘
```

### Price Row Typography

| Element | Font size | Weight | Alignment |
|---|---|---|---|
| Prefix ("Now") | 20px | 700 | Baseline |
| Dollar sign ("$") | 14px | 700 | Superscript (padding-bottom: 6px) |
| Price ("169") | 24px | 700 | Baseline |
| Cents ("98") | 14px | 700 | Superscript (padding-bottom: 8px) |
| Suffix ("/mo") | 14px | 700 | Bottom-aligned |

