## Composition Dependencies

| Dependency | Role |
|---|---|
| `WCPFlag` | Badge overlay (top-left, scaled 0.75) |
| `WCPHeartView` | Favorite toggle (top-right, `size="small"`, `calloutPosition="top"`) |
| `PRODUCT_IMAGES` | Centralized product image URLs |

---

## Layout Specs

| Property | Value |
|---|---|
| Tile background | `var(--ld-semantic-color-surface)` |
| Border radius | `var(--ld-primitive-scale-borderradius-100, 8px)` |
| Image height | `145px` |
| Image padding | `24px 8px 8px` |
| Body padding | `0 8px 8px` |
| Body min-height | `72px` |
| Name line clamp | `1` |

---

## Usage in Category Grids

```tsx
<div className={styles.productGrid}>
  {products.map((product, i) => (
    <WCPItemTile key={i} {...product} />
  ))}
</div>
```

```css
.productGrid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  grid-auto-rows: 1fr;  /* ensures equal tile heights */
  gap: 8px;
}
```

